dct_title_s: Galapagos Islands, Quito & Guayaquil : scale 1:350,000/1:12,400/1:10,000 : Quito region, Guayaquil region / International Travel Maps. (Quito)
dct_description_sm: Relief on Galapagos Islands map shown by contours, gradient tints, hachures, and spot heights. Depths shown by bathymetric tints. Panel title. "© ITMB Publishing. 2022." Galapagos Islands map includes index to tourist attractions, island inset, inset city map of Guayaquil (scale 1:10,000), map of Guayaquil region (scale 1:100,000), notes, and color photographs of wildlife. Quito map oriented with north toward the right. Quito map includes indexes to streets and tourist attractions, map of Quito region (scale 1:800,000), and diagrammatic map of Quito transit system.
